Query Plan
=================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                           |NAME    |
-------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR MERGE SORT          |        |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR               |:EX10001|
|2 |  └─SORT                           |        |
|3 |    └─HASH JOIN                    |        |
|4 |      ├─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |
|5 |      │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY)|:EX10000|
|6 |      │   └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR  |        |
|7 |      │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |t1      |
|8 |      └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR      |        |
|9 |        └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |t2      |
=================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([INTERNAL_FUNCTION(t1.c1, t1.c2, t1.c3, t1.c4, t2.c1, t2.c2, t2.c3, t2.c4)]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      sort_keys([t1.c2, ASC])
  1 - output([t1.c2], [INTERNAL_FUNCTION(t1.c1, t1.c2, t1.c3, t1.c4, t2.c1, t2.c2, t2.c3, t2.c4)]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      dop=1
  2 - output([t1.c2], [t1.c1], [t2.c1], [t2.c2], [t1.c3], [t2.c3], [t1.c4], [t2.c4]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      sort_keys([t1.c2, ASC])
  3 - output([t1.c2], [t1.c1], [t2.c1], [t2.c2], [t1.c3], [t2.c3], [t1.c4], [t2.c4]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      equal_conds([t1.c1 = t2.c1], [t1.c2 = t2.c2], [t1.c3 = t2.c3], [t1.c4 = t2.c4]), other_conds(nil)
  4 - output([t1.c2], [t1.c1], [t1.c3], [t1.c4]), filter(nil), rowset=256
  5 - output([t1.c2], [t1.c1], [t1.c3], [t1.c4]), filter(nil), rowset=256
      (#keys=4, [t1.c2], [t1.c4], [t1.c1], [t1.c3]), dop=1
  6 - output([t1.c2], [t1.c4], [t1.c1], [t1.c3]), filter(nil), rowset=256
